@node MAIN "MO Disk Icons 1.2"

@{line}@{jcenter}@{b}=================
@{line}MO Disk Icons 1.2
@{line}=================@{ub}
@{line}This AmigaGuide document copyright © 1999 by
@{"Mark Knibbs" link Contacting}. Icons are the copyright of their respective
authors.@{par}@{jleft}

Junji Morokuma has made a collection of Macintosh icons for MO disks. These
icons were converted to PNG format by Robert Niessner, and from PNG to IFF-ILBM
by myself. I have written this AmigaGuide document to allow easy viewing.@{par}

Use your favourite image conversion program to convert the IFF-ILBM images to
Workbench icons.@{par}

The original Macintosh-format collection, which may be of interest if you use a
Mac emulator, can be found at:@{code}
@{jcenter}@{fg highlight}ftp://src.doc.ic.ac.uk/packages/info-mac/gui/icon/mo-disk-icons-12.hqx@{fg text}@{par}@{jleft}@{body}

@{code}@{"       Read ME!        " link Read_ME!}

