@node Read_Me-E "Read Me-E"

@{code}=============================================================================

                            Idea's MO Icon Ver1.1

                              by Hideo Hayashi

=============================================================================

· About "Idea's MO Icon"

I created these Icons mostly for myself. So this is freeware. 
But I do not refuse your sending me an e-mail.
You can share them freely to someone who you know.
If you want to reprint them to another site, BBS, network, CD-ROM 
or something like that, tell me about it.

=============================================================================

